<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/23555847-matt-duckworth">Matt Duckworth</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Probably because it is the most realistically depicted and well researched outer space object impact scenario known to man thus far. This book is one <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Probably because it is the most realistically depicted and well researched outer space object impact scenario known to man thus far. This book is one of a kind, definitely deserves to be at the top of a lot of fiction lists. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
